## 6. Security for Production AI Agents

| Threat | Mitigation |
|--------|-----------|
| **Prompt injection** | Validate and sanitise all user inputs; use system prompt guards |
| **Tool misuse** | Restrict tool permissions; validate tool outputs |
| **Data exfiltration** | Restrict agent memory access; audit logs |
| **API key exposure** | Environment variables; secrets manager (AWS Secrets, Vault) |
| **Insecure tool execution** | Sandbox code execution (Docker containers, E2B) |
| **PII in logs** | Scrub logs of personally identifiable information |

